The API fetches the information.

3. What is MCP?

MCP = Model Context Protocol

It is a standard way for AI models to use external tools.

Think of MCP as a USB port for AI.

Example

Your laptop can connect to:

Mouse
Keyboard
Pen Drive

using USB.

Similarly AI can connect to:

Google Docs
Databases
GitHub
Gmail

using MCP.

AI
 │
