One-Line Summary
UCP = The shopping language that lets AI agents understand products and create orders across different merchants.
AP2 = The secure payment system that lets AI agents spend money safely using encryption and user-defined spending limits.

Together, they enable autonomous AI shopping, where an AI can find products, create orders, and pay for them while staying within the user's approved rules.


